{
  "texts": [
    "There are many existing models of disease processes and immune system function that can be used to build MDTs, as mentioned above.",
    "Research is needed to develop a platform for the modular construction of complex MDT models from component models.",
    "Such a platform is essential for achieving the long-term vision of a virtual patient.",
    "A possible approach is proposed in 12, 36.",
    "The data from an individual patient captures different aspects of their characteristics and health status."
  ]
}